*1937-1938: Moshe Rosenberg [http://etzel.org.il/english/people/rosenbrg.htm]</br>
*1938-1941: [[David Raziel]]<ref>Raziel was arrested by the British on May 19, 1939 and was replaced by Hanoch Kalai[http://www.etzel.org.il/english/people/kalai.htm]. On August 31, 1939 Kalai was arrested and Benyamin Zeroni[http://www.etzel.org.il/english/people/zeroni.htm] took his place until Raziel's release and return to the leadership on October 20.</ref></br>
